                    </ul>
                </nav>
                <img src="./pic/proicon.png"  class="profiles" width="27px"></a>
            </div>
            <div class="h-row">
                <div class="h-col-2">
                    <h1>LIVE LIKE YOU WANT</h1>
                    <h2>The Lifestyle You Deserve:<br></h2>
                    <br><p>Everything You Need . All Right Here Modern Amenities , Urban Location , Sophisticated Style Bridging the gap between convenience and luxury . A Higher Quality of Living Dream Big , Live Well.</p>
